Step 2 - Exploring data

Which predictor to keep? Some predictors are non-sensor data (based on the column name) and/or have a too-good-to-be-true correlation with the outcome. In the following plot for instance, X is too correlated with the outcome, timestamp and new_window are not sensor data.

featurePlot(x=trainingraw[,c("X","new_window","cvtd_timestamp", "classe")],
